description: Community-based pack of 30 maps, all with the goal of remaking a multiplayer map from another game as a Quake singleplayer map. The maps use Copper (included) and are connected by a start map (also a remix, of Q3A's The Longest Yard)
notes: This file was repackaged for Quake Injector compatibility.
May require a source port with increased limits / BSP2 support.
title: Remix Jam
